Salesforce Quick Record Details Page Loader
===========================================

Once you have installed the plugin, follow this simple process:
1. Copy in memory the record ID that you want to load into a new Chrome tab
2. Select an existing tab that contains a page of the same Salesforce Org
3. Click the plugin button

You'll see a new Chrome tab that contains the record details page.


How To Install This Plugin
==========================
simply check-out the file "build/sfdcrlb.crx" and double-click it.


